            "creation_date": 1458970681,
            "body": "<p>Previous response: The index page should be \"my index.html\" or \"index.html\".\nIt needs to go right with what is in the servlet.<\/p>\n\n<p>\n    index.html<\/p>\n\n<p>Posting it twice really is the problem. I'm glad this has been resolved. it's helpful to me as well. Thanks<\/p>\n",
